latestIgtvVideos.title: Ahhh!! Go to @irisandromeo! NOW!!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I helped them find all your guys’ shades within their #BESTSKINDAYS skincare/makeup hybrid whiiiiich, isn’t a foundation, because it has so much more going on than just THAT and NOW, starting today, those NEW shades are finally OUT and available to buy! This is after almost 2 years, people! I started wearing #BestSkinDays on my own, and it became one of my favorite things to put on my face. I can say it’s almost what I exclusively wore on a daily basis for all of 2020! @irisandromeo and I joined forces in the way that you fantasize about teaming up with a brand. Naturally, excitedly and un-awkwardly! Lol. A big part of that was through instagram actually. Every single person who worked on this and helped make it happen had such #passion and were so good at their jobs! Everyone really cared that we got this RIGHT! No one wanted anotherrrr thing out there that didn’t live up to the hype or deliver. WHAT’S THE POINT?! We’re too smart and educated now as consumers and just too tired of the phoned in BS. The brand’s founder @michelegough really, reallllly got that and is easily one of the most inspiring and aware people I have ever met in my life. She’s absolutely incredible. I’m so #grateful for this opportunity and that we got the #colors to a place where we were able to take out the guess work and STRESS away from you when trying to find your perfect match! But seriously, getting to this moment became equal parts perfectionism and also, compulsive! LOL. There’s 12 #shades that adapt to suit 36 skin different #tones! I have sooo much more to say, but I’ll shut up! Go check out the NEW #bestskindays shades at #irisandromeo!
#shadesshadesshadesshades #lessmakeupmoreyou
• For 20% off of $50 or more, type in CAROLA20 when you check out at #irisandromeo

latestIgtvVideos.title: Bored in the car before heading to #pioneertown
latestIgtvVideos.caption: might as well make a mascara vid since I was already about to apply it! I really did just grab this new #covergirl mascara, not sponsored. I think it came out in 2020? Idk, I’m late to the game! It’s vegan and supposed to be w/out all the typical crap in it. But ask any makeup artist and they’ll say Cover Girl’s OG orange mascara is one of the best you can buy! Now I’m trying out their blue to see how it holds up! And I never apply mascara without my little brush! Never, ever, ever! Update: I’m a few hours in and it’s legit! Not clumping, flaking, dry or falling yet! #theblackerthebetter #lashblastclean #volumemascara 👁👄👁

latestIgtvVideos.title: I have been sitting on this video since like Aug of 2019
latestIgtvVideos.caption: I sent it to my 4 trusted sources who said it was too long (and it is, lol) and that I sound crazy 🙋🏻‍♀️. I don’t even give a shit anymore, I like it! It’s just me and a friend having a real convo while I did my makeup. So if you like long rants about #hairloss, #hairgrowth, #prp, #hairprp, #melasma, #melasmamustaches, #botox, #fillers, #lasers and a #saggyeyetutorial at the end, then watch on!! 😂😘
